---
import Badge from "./Badge.astro";
import LinkedInIcon from "./icons/LinkedInIcon.astro";
import SocialPill from "./SocialPill.astro";
---

<article
  class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row md:gap-12 max-sm:px-4"
>
  <!-- Image Section with Personal Details -->
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center order-1 md:order-1 space-y-4">
    <!-- Image -->
    <img
      width="200"
      height="200"
      src="/lightPhoto.jpg"
      alt="Me in Sunny day"
      class="object-cover rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-100 to-gray-200 shadow-md ring-2 ring-black/10 dark:ring-white/10 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 dark:hidden block"
    />
    <!-- class="rounded-xl  dark:hidden" -->
    <img
      width="200"
      height="200"
      src="/darkPhoto.jpg"
      alt="Me at night"
      class="object-cover rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br dark:from-yellow-500/10 dark:to-gray-700/30 shadow-md ring-2 ring-black/10 dark:ring-white/10 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105 hidden dark:block"
    />

    <!-- Personal Details -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-2">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-400">Full Stack Developer</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Brisbane, Australia
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <a
          href="mailto:edwinleon@webdevinnovation.com?subject=Potential%Opportunity&body=I%20would%20like%20to%20connect%20with%20you."
          class="hover:underline"
          target="_blank"
        >
          edwinleon@webdevinnovation.com
        </a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">+61 0452 069 981</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Download Resume Button -->
    <Badge href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/edwinleonb/">OPEN TO WORK</Badge>
  </div>

  <!-- Text Section -->
  <div class="order-2 md:order-2 max-w-xl space-y-6">
    <!-- First Paragraph -->
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg">
      Hi, I’m <strong class="text-yellow-400">Edwin León</strong>, a <strong
        >Full Stack Software Developer with over 3 years of experience</strong
      >. Originally from Colombia and now based in Australia, I enjoy <strong
        >building modern, high-performance web applications</strong
      >
      that enhance user experiences and drive business growth. My expertise includes
      <strong>JavaScript, TypeScript, React, Node.js, SAPUI5, and SQL</strong>,
      enabling me to tackle complex technical challenges efficiently.
    </p>

    <!-- Second Paragraph -->
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg">
      Throughout my career, I’ve <strong
        >worked on integrating ERP services into frontend applications</strong
      >,
      <strong>modernising legacy systems</strong>, <strong
        >optimising database performance</strong
      >, and <strong>developing intuitive user interfaces</strong>. I’ve also
      contributed to <strong>seamless CI/CD pipelines</strong> and <strong
        >database migration projects</strong
      >, ensuring robust and efficient solutions for clients.
    </p>

    <!-- Third Paragraph -->
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg">
      Collaboration is at the core of my work, and I thrive in <strong
        >cross-functional teams</strong
      > where I can <strong>mentor others</strong>, share knowledge, and
      contribute to innovative projects. I am committed to <strong
        >continuous learning</strong
      > and staying updated with the latest industry trends, allowing me to deliver
      impactful solutions that meet evolving needs.
    </p>

    <!-- Fourth Paragraph -->
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg">
      Outside of coding, I enjoy <strong
        >participating in tech community events</strong
      >, exploring new ideas, and contributing to meaningful initiatives. Let’s
      connect and <strong>create something extraordinary together!</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</article>
